===Pronunciation===
נשׁא / nâshâ' / naw-shaw'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''נשׁא'''

# To lead astray, that is, (mentally) to delude, or (morally) to seduce: - [[beguile]], deceive, X greatly, X utterly.

